{"tid":1308173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"«致：7月11號晚，在連儂牆只懂圍觀拍片的人»","createTime":"2019-07-11T23:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T13:09:19.000Z","uid":131691,"like":125,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b819dc776626ef2b7d6b661c63d7d0f705233a76","tid":1308173,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:11:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7月11號，又有香港人喺連儂牆被打</span><br />\n<br />\n但係令人痛心嘅，唔係有人俾人打，係有人貼完「支持」上連儂牆後，淨係識拍片+後推<br />\n<br />\n「唔好打呀！」<br />\n「停手呀！」<br />\n唱生日歌<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲說話，打緊人嘅禽獸會識聽嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n一百個電話<br />\n做一百個Facebook live<br />\n有哂證據<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">個黑警會因為咁而幫手嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n唔幫手制服暴徒之餘<br />\n仲要後推<br />\n最後竟然一百個圍觀者<br />\n可以放人走<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得羞恥嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n「支持」嘅語句在連儂牆寫了<br />\n卡，也打了<br />\n到真係需要支持嘅時候<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你做緊啲咩？</span><br />\n<br />\n請停止一切非理性嘅假和平<br />\n因為你所做嘅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實係助長咗暴力</span><br />\n<br />\n政府笑了<br />\n因為完來唔使催淚彈<br />\n已經可以令到香港人骨折<br />\n同時為骨折而感到驕傲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圍觀者嘅潔癖<br />\n遠比藍絲嘅拳頭痛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n烈士都死咗<br />\n而佢哋並唔係為你哋圍觀而死<br />\n請停止用虛偽嘅和平<br />\n辜負壯烈嘅遺願<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長沙灣有南亞裔的真香港人做到了<br />\n你呢？</span></span>"},{"pid":"85e48e03e1c2b02b536eda8beaaf64d6515403b9","tid":1308173,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f061c93771a267351cba0d529c5b92c2fdc03e6","tid":1308173,"uid":86083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:13:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2623d4625e3f07bef4467165f996d5b1defc5f4d","tid":1308173,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b84bbfecc069e48a40b858adc58f7db780771ff","tid":1308173,"uid":152584,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:16:01.000Z","msg":"同612企喺天橋上面班人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72f9cb692f23641491d35109b06a11cdc976542","tid":1308173,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83585841b123bcf129a797f2343aa608399386a","tid":1308173,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:17:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7de5b1fffe97bf8e3e7f913c65b702ceb509fe28","tid":1308173,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dd585f23fad353344b16bb08fa6e298517e4f5","tid":1308173,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ea83312b06007a5b788dbc2570c9a5c87e8029","tid":1308173,"uid":131691,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0b84bbfecc069e48a40b858adc58f7db780771ff","tid":1308173,"uid":152584,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:16:01.000Z","msg":"同612企喺天橋上面班人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:24:33.000Z","msg":"可以鬧<br />\n可以勸<br />\n唔可以笑"},{"pid":"c368efc1966daaf2df115b720e6dd95907176688","tid":1308173,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:30:01.000Z","msg":"見到個個拎住部電話影 我以為自己睇black mirror"},{"pid":"856b857334e24845d6a2f2f7dea7077523f9eb7e","tid":1308173,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:30:46.000Z","msg":"唔好再嘈<br />\n我地無條件撐勇武<br />\n同樣道理<br />\n都無條件撐和理非<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不指責<br />\n大家都係同路人"},{"pid":"757b55ede4eb8bc6e07fdcf8a2717a93e4e250fd","tid":1308173,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:31:16.000Z","msg":"[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb5c5bd80331f1a6a3be74ec4656ea4a7e692378","tid":1308173,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"856b857334e24845d6a2f2f7dea7077523f9eb7e","tid":1308173,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:30:46.000Z","msg":"唔好再嘈<br />\n我地無條件撐勇武<br />\n同樣道理<br />\n都無條件撐和理非<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不指責<br />\n大家都係同路人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"問題係而家大埔嗰種和理非已經係幫敵人助攻<br />\n<br />\n仲有，成日講嘅be water，而家根本背道而馳<br />\n大埔嘅和理非應該向金鐘連儂牆嘅和理非學習<br />\n六月金鐘個連儂牆被拆過，連烈士祭壇都拆過<br />\n金鐘佢哋真係識be water<br />\n唔會挨打咁死守，反而係第二日重建"},{"pid":"5a3da27f446d645273d51653a28a5b9ad6e2befa","tid":1308173,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:38:19.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主